Class PlacedGearMachine

  • java.lang.Object
    • gears.sidescroller.world.core.ObjectInWorld
      • gears.sidescroller.world.machines.AbstractMachine
        • gears.sidescroller.world.machines.GearMachine
          • gears.sidescroller.world.machines.PlacedGearMachine
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Collidable, Interactable, PowerProvidingMachine

    public class PlacedGearMachine
extends GearMachine
implements Interactable
    A PlacedGearMachine is simply a GearMachine a Player has placed via a GearItem. I don't particularly like how I'm using an entirely different class for this. The Player can pick this back up by interacting with it.
